        "TileImage": "$($repository 885abce1-e07b-41f7-9bf1-492865c1c3e8).Image",
        "Description": "47, \r\rThe ICA has determined that their agents, while operating effectively, are using the same kill methods every mission. They have asked all agents to prove that they are versatile assassins still- if you fail this mission.... well... just don&apos;t fail. Use a different kill method for each target. \r\rYour fate at the ICA is in your hands. \rI will leave you to prepare. Make me proud. \r\r-Diana",
